LEAD FROM WITHIN

The days of following a leader are over. 

I prefer to make a distinction. 

There are #PIONEERS in the new model. 

The old model would have you believe there is a leader, an Alpha male (or female) who knows better than you do. 

But this antiquated philosophy is based upon a patriarchal system where citizens feel victimized & need someone to protect them and come to their rescue. 

Explore the truth of this inside of yourself & you’ll find a frequency of fear undermining everything you attempt to move towards & create for yourself. 

So the solution, of course, is looking outside of yourself for someone stronger, more capable. 

But that person only represents one thing you don’t believe you have nor are willing to develop. 

That word is #Confidence.

Many have had great ideas filled with excitement & hope. Only to watch their plans fizzle out when motivation dries up. 

That is because excitement is an emotion. Fleeting by its very nature. Unstable in its very structure. 

Emotions are outside of you. Something you’re affected by. 

Maybe it’s hope. But hope is also temporary. 

Confidence is a feeling. 

The former would have you act from impetuousness and a structure that is volatile. 

The latter propels you to move through life with an inner knowing based on a solid #connection to your core—the very truth of your Being—giving rise to purpose, real power that comes from within, as well as clarity & vision from your heart’s desire. 

I detest war, so it’s not often I make reference to the armed forces. 

War is only a necessary evil as long as we’re asleep to a bigger vision for humanity. 

Mark my words, an army of #love is coming 💛 

And it includes you & your contribution to this new reality. 

We will lead ourselves into our own true destiny finally bringing an end to the madness in the world born out of sick minds disconnected from the person’s heart & real humanity. 

The #revolution is underway. 

Will you stand back and watch as a spectator? 

Indifferent to the outcome?

Or will you rise up & take your place within the crowd to give your gift through being a fully expressed human? 👑

Be a Warrior of the Light ⭐️

#inspiration

A few months ago I had a decision to make. 

Do I continue on a path that's not aligned with my highest purpose? 

Or do I take a risk and go to a place I'd never been before…

I decided to double down on environment. 

And what I found was a rejuvenated importance in community and connection,

which has not only opened up new financial doors 🚪,

incredible opportunities for internal and external growth,

yet also a renewed sense of peace with my purpose and where I'm going in my life. 

You see when you surround yourself with the right environment of people,

who are ambitious, 

who are leaders,

who share like minded values with you..

You start to amplify your vibration, 

just by being around them. 

It goes without saying…

It would be my honor to host you in Tulum for weekend immersion, 

or our upcoming men's retreat. The Conscious Business Mastermind 🤘🏾🚀

This October 26 to the 29th. 

We will be going on an inner journey around our limiting beliefs, 

rewiring our nervous system and our subconscious. 

Overcoming impostor syndrome while reframing our relationship with money,

and up leveling our brands and sales process simultaneously. 

If you feel called to join us on this mission, 

we have one spot remaining for a male entrepreneur who is currently crushing it in his business,

and wants to take his game to the next level. 

I appreciate you and support you for wanting to be a part of my network and my community. 

I look forward to see you soon. 

Dave

I don’t know about you but for me so much is going on in my world right now. 

Between community, business, family, friends, my own desires, 

It’s not easy to always stay focused. 

That’s why coming back to the breath is so important. 

Taking time to do nothing is vital,

and remembering how far we’ve come on the journey is essential. 

If you don’t take time to show yourself gratitude and appreciation, 

you will forget not only about source energy, 

but also about how incredible of a human being, you truly are. 

In order to be a successful entrepreneur, 

you’ve got to have gratitude and appreciation for your journey. 

It’s not healthy to always be seeking and looking outside, YOU must go within. 

Many of the guys I work with really struggle in this area. 

They’re constantly looking for the next thing, the next shiny object,

the next business coaching program or retreat,

or free marketing asset,

rather than remembering that You are already whole, more than good enough,

and valuing yourself is a huge part of this game of life.

And the more you value yourself, the more you can invest in amazing coaches and masterminds and programs. 

The more you can invest in running paid ads, and traveling the world hiring photographers and videographers,

so take a deep breath and just remember with all that’s going on outside, 

look within.

First off, let's get down to the nitty gritty, who is a conscious entrepreneur? 

A conscious entrepreneur, is someone that is creating impact in the world and doing it from a place of service. 

A leader that wants to support, bring light to the world, and has a positive message to help people to change their lives! 

Could be in their business, could be in their relationships, could be in their finances, it could be in their health or mindset. 

Doesn't matter in the end of the day. 

People all want the same thing. 

But many of us are at different points along our journey. 

And so for people who are further ahead, we have an obligation to lead by example, to rise up, and to share our message and our powerful energy with others so we can empower them to feel and be and do the same. 

Unconscious entrepreneurs are the ones that just look at you as a number. 

Just wants your money. 

Don't actually deliver on their promises, and make excuses and blame other people. 

Rather than taking ownership and responsibility of the position that they're currently in. 

Unconscious entrepreneurs like to shame and cancel others pushing out a aura that they're better than someone else. 

When in reality, we are all just a mirror for one another at the end of the day. 

Also, conscious entrepreneurs pay people back on time, usually investing upfront because they know there is a financial incentive to pay upfront. 

And to not wait and wait and wait and renege on agreements because it only creates negative karma that takes months if not years, or lifetime to clean up. 

I love working with conscious entrepreneurs because at the end of the day, the ones who are working on themselves are the ones who succeed the most in their business. 

If you're a conscious entrepreneur, that is you are actually working on your inner work, your shadow work, your healing journey, and really taking your life seriously. 

Hit me up because I might be able to help you actualize your goals in a big fucking way. 

- Dave 

#business #alignment #coaching

Let’s talk about balance. 

Most entrepreneurs that I meet are completely out of it. 

They are constantly distracted by new shiny objects…posting content in the wrong places with the wrong messaging that doesn’t actually attract their ideal clients so and focused on things in their business that aren’t actually generating revenue. 

So how do we change it? 

First, we’ve got to diagnose the problem before we can provide a solution. 

But once we find the problem, we must surrender to it. 

We must rewire our thought process around it so that we can create the needed discipline to transform that challenge into a triumph. 

I work with conscious entrepreneurs one on one my program “elevate” to help them rewire their thought processes around their content, their team and their offer. 

This is something that you’d like help with. 

Drop me a message with the word elevate. 

It’d be my honor to serve you and help you to build a loyal community that generates you 10 to 50k of monthly recurring revenue doing something that you love while creating massive impact in the world. 

I’m Dave Gold, a Conscious Business Coach, and I help entrepreneurs level up their sales and marketing in under 90 days. 

I’ll see you on the other side. Peace ✌🏽
